"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:5.20.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">5.20.1</span> 標題：碗（bowl）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אַגָּן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’agan)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:3\">SNG 7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:24\">ISA 22:24</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： גֻּלָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： gulah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:6\">ECC 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:2\">ZEC 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:3\">ZEC 4:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מִזְרָק</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mizraq)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:6\">AMO 6:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מִשְׁאֶרֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mish’ereth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:28\">EXO 7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:34\">EXO 12:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:5\">DEU 28:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:17\">DEU 28:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： צְלֹחִית</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tslochith)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:20\">2KI 2:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἀργύρωμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： argurōma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt12:1\">JDT 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt15:11\">JDT 15:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc15:32\">1MA 15:32</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ὁλκεῖον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： holkeion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt15:11\">JDT 15:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σκάφη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： skafē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:33\">BEL 1:33</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： τρύβλιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： trublion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:23\">MAT 26:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:20\">MRK 14:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir31:14\">SIR 31:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： φιάλη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： fialē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:8\">REV 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:7\">REV 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:1\">REV 16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:2\">REV 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:3\">REV 16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:4\">REV 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:8\">REV 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:10\">REV 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:12\">REV 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:17\">REV 16:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:1\">REV 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:9\">REV 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:3\">EXO 27:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:23\">EXO 38:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:14\">NUM 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:13\">NUM 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:19\">NUM 7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:25\">NUM 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:31\">NUM 7:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:37\">NUM 7:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:43\">NUM 7:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:49\">NUM 7:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:55\">NUM 7:55</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:61\">NUM 7:61</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:67\">NUM 7:67</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:73\">NUM 7:73</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:79\">NUM 7:79</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:84\">NUM 7:84</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:85\">NUM 7:85</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:26\">1KI 7:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:31\">1KI 7:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:36\">1KI 7:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:14\">2KI 12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:14\">2KI 25:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:15\">2KI 25:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:17\">1CH 28:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:8\">2CH 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:21\">2CH 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:31\">PRO 23:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:13\">SNG 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song6:2\">SNG 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:18\">JER 52:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:15\">ZEC 9:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:20\">ZEC 14:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:22\">1MA 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd2:10\">1ES 2:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： χρύσωμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chrusōma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc15:32\">1MA 15:32</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>碗是一種凹形餐具，用來盛放、烹煮食物或液體，直徑和深度差別很大。碗通常是用燒製的黏土做成的，但<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:8\">REV 5:8</a> 特別提到金子做的碗。由於碗的大小和深度頗不相同，而杯子又通常沒有把手，所以較小的碗和杯子看起來基本上沒有什麼區別。<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">5.20.3 杯子 (cup)&lt;REALIA:5.20.3&gt;</a> 下的第一個插圖也繪出了碗。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:2\">ZEC 4:2</a> 中，讀者可能不會立時明白碗（希伯來文<em>gulah</em> ；《和修》「燈座」）的用途。我們建議翻譯者借鑒<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ，譯為「頂上有用來裝油的碗」。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:6\">AMO 6:6</a> 中提到的碗是專門用來喝酒的（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">5.20.3 杯子 (cup)&lt;REALIA:5.20.3&gt;</a> ）。翻譯這節經文時，可能要根據當地文化做出適當的調整。例如，在一些文化中，可以使用表示某種大葫蘆的詞語，或者使用葫蘆的統稱，並用「大」和「滿」等詞語加以修飾。</p>\n<p>希伯來文<em>mish’ereth</em> 指的是一種大碗，用來揉麵和發酵，然後進行烘烤。大多數譯本譯為「揉麵碗」（“kneading bowls”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> ）或「揉麵槽」（“kneading troughs”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> ）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 的“baking pans”（「烤盤」）可能會誤導讀者。如果沒有表示這種碗的專門詞語，或者這種碗不為人所熟知，翻譯者可以遵循<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 的範例，譯為“bowls of bread dough”（「麵團碗」）。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:23\">MAT 26:23</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:20\">MRK 14:20</a> 中，希臘文<em>trublion</em> 可以理解為一句慣用語的一部分，這個慣用語的字面意思是，「和某人一起把手伸進碗裡」。大多數譯本基本上是按照字面來翻譯這個慣用語的，但這可能會讓讀者產生誤解，以為人是把手指放到碗裡，而不是用手拿著食物在碗裡蘸一下。如果翻譯者想要在某種程度上直譯這個慣用語，最好譯成「和某人一起把食物在碗裡蘸一下」，或「一起把食物在醬汁裡蘸一下」。我們建議把這個慣用語譯為：「和某人分享餐食」，或「和某人一起吃飯」。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:20\">MRK 14:20</a> 的後半節可譯為，「一個正和我一起在這個盤子裡吃飯的人」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ），或「正和我一起吃飯的一個人」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Living Translation\">NLT</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc15:32\">1MA 15:32</a> ：希臘文<em>chrusōma</em> 的字面意思是「黃金物件」。然而，該詞在這裡指的是金或鍍金的餐具。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 譯為“gold[en] bowls”（「金碗」）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
